## ============================================================
## .gitignore — FundiLink by ZulTek
## Covers: .NET, Node/React/Vite, VS, VS Code, Rider, secrets
## ============================================================

## ── Secrets and Environment Files (NEVER commit these) ──────
.env
.env.*
.env.local
.env.development
.env.staging
.env.production
*.env
secrets.json
appsettings.Production.json
appsettings.Staging.json
appsettings.Local.json
**/appsettings.Production.json
**/appsettings.Staging.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

## Allow committed example/template env files (no real secrets)
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example
**/*.pfx
**/*.p12
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.cer
**/*.crt

## ── .NET User Secrets (local only, never commit) ───────────
**/secrets.json
%APPDATA%/Microsoft/UserSecrets/
~/.microsoft/usersecrets/

## ── .NET Build Output ───────────────────────────────────────
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.sln.docstates
.vs/
_ReSharper*/
*.DotSettings.user
TestResults/
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage/
coverage-report/

## ── .NET NuGet ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/
!packages/repositories.config
*.nuspec
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## ── .NET Publish ─────────────────────────────────────────────
**/publish/
**/published/

## ── Entity Framework Migrations (keep migrations, ignore leftovers) ─
# Keep: Migrations/*.cs and Migrations/*Designer.cs
# Ignore EF tools temp output only — do NOT ignore the Migrations folder

